"title": "5159: hearing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5159: hearing",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In Scripture, both physical hearing and spiritual apprehension. God hears the prayers of his people and the cry of the oppressed. People must hear and respond to God's word.</p>\n<h2>Divine hearing</h2>\n<h3>God hears the prayers of his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:7\">2SA 22:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:4\">PSA 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:24\">ISA 65:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:41-John11:42\">JHN 11:41–11:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:12\">1PE 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:15\">PSA 34:15</a></p>\n<h3>God hears the grumbling of his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1\">NUM 11:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:7-Exod16:9\">EXO 16:7–16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:11-Exod16:12\">EXO 16:11–16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:1-Num12:2\">NUM 12:1–12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:27\">NUM 14:27</a></p>\n<h3>God hears the cry of the oppressed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:7\">EXO 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:9\">PSA 94:9</a></p>\n<h3>God does not hear the unrighteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:2\">ISA 59:1–59:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:18\">PSA 66:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:11\">JER 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:14\">JER 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:18\">EZK 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:23\">AMO 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:31\">JHN 9:31</a></p>\n<h3>Other gods cannot hear</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:26-1Kgs18:27\">1KI 18:26–18:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:6\">PSA 115:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:17\">PSA 135:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:7\">ISA 46:7</a></p>\n<h2>Hearing the word of God</h2>\n<h3>The importance of hearing God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:1\">DEU 5:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13\">EPH 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:1\">DEU 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:4\">JER 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:2\">JER 7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:2\">MIC 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:16-Matt13:17\">MAT 13:16–13:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:23-Luke10:24\">LUK 10:23–10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:17\">ROM 10:17</a></p>\n<h3>Having ears to hear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:15\">MAT 11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:9\">MAT 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:9\">MRK 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:23\">MRK 4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:8\">LUK 8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:11\">REV 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:17\">REV 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:29\">REV 2:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:6\">REV 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:13\">REV 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:22\">REV 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>The gospel must not only be heard but accepted and acted on</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:2\">HEB 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:14-Mark4:20\">MRK 4:14–4:20</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19-Matt13:23\">MAT 13:19–13:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:11-Luke8:15\">LUK 8:11–8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:13\">ROM 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:2\">GAL 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5\">GAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22-Jas1:24\">JAS 1:22–1:24</a></p>\n<h3>It is God who grants effective hearing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:14\">ACT 16:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:12\">PRO 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:5\">ISA 50:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13-2Thess2:14\">2TH 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Some people refuse to hear God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:10\">JER 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:18-Isa42:20\">ISA 42:18–42:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:2\">EZK 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51\">ACT 7:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:4\">2TI 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>God denies the effective hearing of his word to those who stubbornly resist him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:10-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:10–13:15</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:10-Mark4:12\">MRK 4:10–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:9-Luke8:10\">LUK 8:9–8:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:9–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:43\">JHN 8:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:26-Acts28:27\">ACT 28:26–28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:8\">ROM 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:4\">DEU 29:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:10\">ISA 29:10</a></p>\n<h2>The first Christians witnessed to what they had heard</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:14-Acts22:15\">ACT 22:14–22:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:20\">ACT 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3\">HEB 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1\">1JN 1:1</a></p>\n<h2>Physical hearing was restored by Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:35-Mark7:37\">MRK 7:35–7:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:5\">MAT 11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:22\">LUK 7:22</a></p>\n<h2>The dead will hear the voice of the Son of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:25\">JHN 5:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:28-John5:29\">JHN 5:28–5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:43-John11:44\">JHN 11:43–11:44</a></p>",
